description: It is a movie-quiz that involves individuals of all ages. An individual will be asked five questions and is supposed to make a correct guess of the movie, when Alexa prompts with a famous dialogues of the movie to be guessed. On a correct guess, the individual will be awarded a point by Alexa. The individual with the highest number of correct guesses will be the winner!
name: MovQuiz
shortDescription: It is a fun-time hollywood movie quiz.
